    "## Conclusion and Further Exploration\n",
    "\n",
    "In this notebook, we have explored several aspects of the **PiSequence** project:\n",
    "- We generated 1 million decimals of π and saved them to `data/pi_decimals.txt`.\n",
    "- We searched for specific sequences using `sequence_search.py`, finding known sequences like “314159” and confirming that unlikely sequences like “999999999” are not present.\n",
    "- We analyzed the frequency of digits using `frequency_analysis.py`, visualizing the results with a histogram and confirming a near-uniform distribution.\n",
    "- We searched for meaningful sequences using `meaningful_sequences.py`, finding short sequences like prime numbers but not longer ones like a birth date.\n",
    "- We validated the sequence search functionality with unit tests using `test_search.py`.\n",
